  "Description": {
    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>The armoured beast within - part crystal, part flesh - rattles gently against the egg.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within has the genetic potential to be deeply <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">devoted</span> to protecting its master.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一颗活生生的受精卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已可孵化！</span><br><br>里面寄宿着一头由水晶与肉体组成的装甲野兽，此刻它正在卵中轻轻翻动。<br><br>根据扫描结果显示，里面的生物拥有特殊的基因潜质，如果好好培养，日后将会无比<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">热忱</span>地保护自己的主人。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "有生命、可孵化的蛋，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">且即將孵化！</span><br><br>內部的裝甲野獸是部分水晶、部分血肉，正微微碰撞著蛋殼。<br><br>掃描結果顯示，該生物可能擁有以下形容的大小及特徵：極度<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">忠心</span>並會保護主人。"
  },
